---
const lineUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_LINE_URL || '#';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();

const courseShortcuts = [
  { href: '/courses', label: '所有課程' },
  { href: '/courses?grade=高中', label: '高中數理' },
  { href: '/courses?grade=國中', label: '國中理化' },
  { href: '/teachers', label: '師資介紹' },
  { href: '/posts', label: '學習筆記' },
];
---

<footer class="mt-24 bg-cream/60 paper-grain border-t border-cream">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 lg:px-8 lg:py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">賈伯斯數理教室</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
          嘉義在地的精英小班補習機構，由台清交資歷師資領軍，專攻國中至高中數理科目。
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-charcoal/80">
          <span class="block">嘉義市東區康樂街 10 號</span>
          <span class="block">電話：(05)223-0303</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-espresso uppercase">
          課程快捷
        </h4>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
          {
            courseShortcuts.map((c) => (
              <li>
                <a href={c.href} class="text-charcoal hover:text-espresso">
                  {c.label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-espresso uppercase">
          聯絡與社群
        </h4>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href={lineUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-charcoal hover:text-espresso">
              LINE 官方帳號
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="text-charcoal hover:text-espresso">Facebook（待補）</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="text-charcoal hover:text-espresso">Instagram（待補）</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/contact" class="text-charcoal hover:text-espresso">聯絡我們</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-cream/80 text-xs text-charcoal/60 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between gap-2">
      <span>&copy; {year} 賈伯斯數理教室. All rights reserved.</span>
      <span>嘉義 · 東區 · 康樂街</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
